1
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,560
How is it?

2
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,280
Are they back?

3
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,000
No.

4
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:39,800
Were they acting

5
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,480
strangely today?

6
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,440
They seemed fine.

7
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:42,880
I didn't notice anything odd.

8
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:45,880
Director Xiaofeng.

9
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,480
I called Dongzi,

10
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,400
but he won't answer.

11
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,560
I fell asleep earlier.

12
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,520
I don't know

13
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,200
when they left.

14
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:51,840
It's okay.

15
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,480
We'll look for them.

16
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,480
Don't worry about it.

17
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,160
Go back and rest.

18
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,520
Keep calling him.

19
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,160
Take another look at this.

20
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,240
Yes, yes.

21
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,000
That's him.

22
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,480
That's his girlfriend beside him.

23
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,520
They left through the north gate.

24
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,120
This is bad.

25
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,160
Once he's out of the hospital,

26
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:18,160
he'll be hard to find.

27
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,440
Wasn't he in the ward?

28
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,440
How did he just disappear?

29
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,040
Three hours doesn't count as missing.

30
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:24,160
We're doing everything we can.

31
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,560
Then where was his primary nurse?

32
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,040
Hello?

33
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:30,760
Hello, Director.

34
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,040
The surveillance footage shows

35
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,720
Lu Dadong and Liang Mei

36
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,800
leaving through the north gate.

37
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:34,920
The guard remembers him.

38
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:36,560
He said they got on a bus,

39
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,160
but he doesn't know

40
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:38,720
which one.

41
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:39,560
Go with Security

42
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,520
to the shops by the hospital entrance.

43
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,080
See what you can do.

44
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:41,880
Check if any cameras

45
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:42,520
caught them.

46
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,440
Forget Security. There's no time.

47
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,080
Call the police.

48
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:47,800
We're not there yet.

49
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,160
We have a lead now.

50
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,080
Let's follow it first.

51
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:52,040
He's in critical condition.

52
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,160
If anything happens outside,

53
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:53,600
what then?

54
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,160
Who's responsible?

55
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:54,880
They're back. They're back.

56
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,880
It's fine. I've got it.

57
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,520
It's okay.

58
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,680
Where did you go?

59
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,000
Why didn't you answer your phone?

60
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,200
Everyone was frantic.

61
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,120
My phone died and shut off.

62
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:05,800
I'm sorry.

63
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,600
You can't leave during hospitalization.

64
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,480
Didn't you know that?

65
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:10,800
No.

66
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,480
I really didn't know.

67
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,160
Then... I'm sorry.

68
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:15,680
Sorry.

69
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,520
Well, I...

70
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,880
We went to get married.

71
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,800
Director Zhou. Director Lin.

72
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:22,880
I have a family now.

73
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:35,600
Director Zhou.

74
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,800
I can sign for him now.

75
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:45,880
Breathe.

76
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,080
Everything looks normal.

77
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,080
No problems for now.

78
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:05,800
Well...

79
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,160
We caused everyone trouble.

80
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,280
It just happened

81
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,760
both our phones died.

82
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,880
We didn't know we couldn't go out.

83
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,240
Don't run off again, okay?

84
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,080
This isn't about whether

85
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:19,920
you caused us trouble.

86
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,800
Your current condition

87
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:22,840
can't afford any accident.

88
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,680
Understand?

89
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,560
I understand.

90
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,600
I won't run off again.

91
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,680
I don't dare anymore.

92
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,400
How do you feel now?

93
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,800
Feel?

94
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,040
How else would I feel?

95
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,400
Happy, of course.

96
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,160
I'm not asking about your mood.

97
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,120
I mean your body.

98
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:42,840
My body?

99
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:44,840
Nothing feels too bad.

100
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,720
Just a little tired.

101
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,800
Then lie down right away.

102
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,040
Okay.

103
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:50,920
Tired?

104
00:04:51,080 --> 00:04:51,480
A little.

105
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,160
It's fine.

106
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:53,880
I'm okay.

107
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,480
Be extra careful these two days.

108
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,720
Stay in bed and rest more.

109
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,480
Xiaorui.

110
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,240
Keep an eye on him for me too.

111
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,480
I didn't expect them to marry

112
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,200
just so she could sign.

113
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:09,720
It's actually touching.

114
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:10,800
It is.

115
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,040
Why didn't Lu Dadong

116
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,000
know his condition

117
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,040
meant he couldn't go out?

118
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,000
Was the admission briefing done properly?

119
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,600
At first I really thought

120
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,880
a family member had taken him for a test.

121
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,040
Level-two nursing patient.

122
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,240
Rounds every two hours.

123
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,200
Observe changes in condition.

124
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:29,080
Monitor vital signs.

125
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:29,680
Did you do all that?

126
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,360
I...

127
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:31,920
And you still laughed in there?

128
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,240
Have you thought about it?

129
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,360
If something really happened

130
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,120
when he went out,

131
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,360
the responsibility would be yours.

132
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,800
Director Lin is right.

133
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:42,360
No matter how busy you are,

134
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,160
necessary procedures

135
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,240
cannot be neglected.

136
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:45,160
And this whole matter...

137
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,760
Go back to work first.

138
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,440
I'll talk to them.

139
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:52,800
Fine.

140
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:53,800
You're the director.

141
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,720
You want to protect your own,

142
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,400
but this is serious.

143
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,680
Don't try to smooth it over

144
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,360
by sending me away.

145
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:09,440
Come with me.

146
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,120
Director.

147
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,120
I really did make rounds.

148
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,400
It's just that the nurses' station

149
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,560
had too many people coming and going.

150
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,160
I couldn't watch every single person.

151
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,160
The round was

152
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,800
just a little over two hours late.

153
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,120
Then he was gone.

154
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,040
What about the admission briefing?

155
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:34,760
Director.

156
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,200
This time,

157
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,120
it was indeed our mistake.

158
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,760
Xiaojing and I are both responsible.

159
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,400
We'll strengthen

160
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,040
education and management in this area.

161
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,600
I know you work hard.

162
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,440
You're understaffed and overloaded,

163
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,760
but that's no excuse for mistakes.

164
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,920
Rounds and briefing weren't done properly.

165
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,080
You know that yourself.

166
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,200
This definitely counts as an incident.

167
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,440
We understand.

168
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,400
This time,

169
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,000
it really was our fault.

170
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,720
We know we were wrong.

171
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,880
I'm sorry, Director.

172
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,360
You don't need to apologize to me.

173
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,560
Start checking immediately

174
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,400
whether anything else

175
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,440
was missed with the patient

176
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,120
and fix it right away.

177
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,440
Okay.

178
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:15,560
Also,

179
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,400
Head Nurse Shen

180
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,480
will be back from training soon.

181
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,760
I have to tell her

182
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,560
what happened today.

183
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,240
As for

184
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,800
specific disciplinary measures,

185
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,400
she'll tell you herself.

186
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,920
We understand, Director.

187
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,880
We understand.

188
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,120
Director.

189
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,080
Do we really have to tell the head nurse?

190
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:40,880
What else?

191
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,400
You haven't met Head Nurse Shen yet, right?

192
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,800
No, but I know her.

193
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,480
Head Nurse Shen Yaqin.

194
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,880
Not long after I went to Guizhou,

195
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,280
she replaced Head Nurse Yu.

196
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,840
She's a veteran at Dongli.

197
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:53,920
She used to be

198
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:54,520
in the ICU.

199
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:55,800
Director Cui personally

200
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,520
transferred her here.

201
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:57,600
Right.

202
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,680
She was brought in to hold the line.

203
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,240
Head Nurse Shen

204
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,480
is very strict.

205
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,040
All the nurses are afraid of her.

206
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,680
So am I.

207
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,880
Then she should know even more.

208
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,400
I thought with the head nurse away,

209
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,280
we could dodge this bullet.

210
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,480
But he's actually going

211
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,680
to report us to her.

212
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,160
Isn't this just a new official

213
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,480
flexing his authority?

214
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,560
Are you upset because he was harsh,

215
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,480
or because he was right?

216
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,480
Sister Yalan.

217
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,720
You forgot the admission briefing.

218
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:27,920
That's a fact.

219
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,480
And the rounds were late.

220
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,480
That's a fact too.

221
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,800
You were caught out.

222
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,720
You can't say it's unfair.

223
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,280
How many times have I told you?

224
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,720
Be more careful at work.

225
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:39,000
Let's see if you remember this time.

226
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:40,880
Besides,

227
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,120
Director Zhou

228
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,240
saved you some face

229
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,920
in front of Director Lin.

230
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,760
If the head nurse were here,

231
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,160
you'd be in even worse trouble.

232
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,160
That Director Lin is annoying too.

233
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,600
Cardiac surgery is now meddling

234
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,400
in cardiology matters.

235
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,040
Long arms and a long mouth.

236
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,160
Say less of that from now on.

237
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,920
We're all in the same Heart Center.

238
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,160
In theory,

239
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,480
we're one family.

240
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:06,360
Director Zhou values that most.

241
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:07,360
Right.

242
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:08,920
The joint clinic is starting soon.

243
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:09,720
You didn't know?

244
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,400
Sister Yalan.

245
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,080
Do you think Director Zhou's joint clinic

246
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,080
can really get off the ground?

247
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,280
I heard

248
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,360
Director Cui is being transferred.

249
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,800
Whether the Heart Center

250
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:22,840
will even stay is still uncertain.

251
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,920
And they're talking about a joint clinic?

252
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:25,760
Missy,

253
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:26,800
you should

254
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,240
worry about yourself first.

255
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:31,600
Get back to work.

256
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:32,840
Your Sister Xiaomei

257
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,800
Xiaomei won't let me move around,

258
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,160
but since we're wardmates

259
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,800
brought together by fate,

260
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,240
I have to hand out the wedding candy myself.

261
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,040
Thank you, Dongzi.

262
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:40,880
I get some too?

263
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,200
Thank you. Thank you.

264
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,360
I'm so happy today.

265
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,240
He doesn't look like decent people.

266
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,080
Who knows what else he's got.

267
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:52,560
What are you saying?

268
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,280
Who's not decent?

269
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,600
I earn my money with my own hands,

270
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:58,560
fair and square.

271
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,400
Go get water.

272
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:02,800
What's wrong?

273
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:03,840
Director Lin.

274
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:05,480
Director.

275
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:07,200
Dadong.

276
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:07,840
I'm sorry.

277
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,000
I'll go get water.

278
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:14,840
Director Lin.

279
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:19,480
Thank you.

280
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,400
What are you doing?

281
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,120
I'll get you another one. Come on.

282
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:21,680
No need.

283
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,200
Happy wedding.

284
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:27,880
Dongzi.

285
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,280
Ignore her.

286
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:31,000
Don't let her spoil the mood.

287
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,720
It won't. Stuff like this...

288
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,680
Let me tell you, Rui.

289
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,720
If it were the old me,

290
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,360
I definitely would've lost it.

291
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,040
Really.

292
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,800
But now it's different.

293
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,120
I have a family.

294
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,440
I'm married.

295
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,080
I have your Sister Xiaomei.

296
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,480
So I won't take it to heart.

297
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,800
That's so cool.

298
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,360
Right, Yi?

299
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,600
You've never seen

300
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:52,200
anyone run out of a hospital

301
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,160
to get married, have you?

302
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:54,800
Not before.

303
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:55,800
Now I have.

304
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,600
Big Winter Melon.

305
00:10:59,800 --> 00:11:00,200
Actually,

306
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,360
let me tell you,

307
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,360
a long time ago,

308
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,800
I already wanted to marry Xiaomei.

309
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,160
I'd been saving up.

310
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,880
Didn't expect she'd bring it up first.

311
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,240
You proposed?

312
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,680
Come on, have some candy.

313
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,280
Have some wedding candy.

314
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:18,920
Thank you. Thank you.

315
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:19,280
Have some candy.

316
00:11:19,560 --> 00:11:19,880
Here.

317
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:20,760
Thank you.

318
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,560
So you rushed

319
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,160
to get married

320
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,360
just so you could

321
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,080
sign for him?

322
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,200
What about Dadong's family?

323
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,800
His mom died early.

324
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,160
He hasn't contacted his dad in years.

325
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,280
My parents both passed away a few years ago too.

326
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:37,840
Have some candy.

327
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:38,880
Have some candy.

328
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,520
Thank you.

329
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,040
I figured,

330
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,440
marriage is simple.

331
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,040
If he wants to marry

332
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,480
and I want to marry him,

333
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,480
we can decide for ourselves.

334
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,920
When my brother died,

335
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:52,880
I was only seven or eight.

336
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:55,480
But you still had to live.

337
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,120
What did you do?

338
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,000
I collected scrap.

339
00:11:59,160 --> 00:11:59,800
When I got older,

340
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,240
I did petty theft and things like that.

341
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,440
I did all kinds of stuff.

342
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:04,800
Every now and then,

343
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:05,600
I'd end up at the station,

344
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,480
like I was checking in.

345
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:08,280
For quite a long time,

346
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,880
I thought

347
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:10,560
I was trash myself.

348
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:12,360
Really.

349
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,720
Then I met Xiaomei.

350
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,680
Suddenly you feel

351
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:23,440
you have a home,

352
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,600
someone wants you.

353
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,080
And right then I thought,

354
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:29,480
I...

355
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:30,880
I had to settle down.

356
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,440
I had to earn money properly.

357
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:33,680
You know,

358
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,920
turn over a new leaf.

359
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:35,440
After that,

360
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:37,040
all those illegal things,

361
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,000
I stopped doing them.

362
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,920
See that, Yi?

363
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,880
That's the power of love.

364
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,800
What kind of phrase is that?

365
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:56,160
Director Lin.

366
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,800
I only have one wish now.

367
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:58,800
Get treated properly.

368
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:01,000
Get better as soon as possible.

369
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,520
Then once I'm out,

370
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:03,440
I'll earn more money.

371
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,600
I'll buy Xiaomei a ring.

372
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,400
Then we'll have a wedding.

373
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:07,560
Then have two kids.

374
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,000
A son and a daughter.

375
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:10,840
Sounds good.

376
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,800
You've got big dreams.

377
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,280
Of course I do.

378
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:25,920
Can't a man dream?

379
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:28,000
That's for sure, right?

380
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,800
Congratulations. Congratulations.

381
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:37,680
Thank you.

382
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:38,280
Thank you.

383
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,760
You're busy.

384
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,840
I won't bother you.

385
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,080
Carry on.

386
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:43,480
Oh my goodness.

387
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:44,160
Look at them.

388
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:44,480
So nice.

389
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,880
Um...

390
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:55,840
I want to thank

391
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:57,160
the doctors

392
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,600
and the nurses.

393
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,520
Dadong and I

394
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,200
came here from out of town to work.

395
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,560
In this city,

396
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:05,360
we don't have relatives or friends.

397
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,720
Just now I saw you

398
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:07,520
put in so much effort

399
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,680
to find Dadong.

400
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:18,480
Thank you.

401
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:13,760
Dongzi.

402
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,560
What bad thing are you doing

403
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:18,360
behind Sister Xiaomei's back?

404
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:29,120
You can't smoke in the hospital.

405
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:30,080
I know. I know.

406
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:31,560
It's empty.

407
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:33,800
I'm just smelling it.

408
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:39,440
It's my first time hospitalized.

409
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:41,760
When I can't sleep,

410
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:42,800
I just want a cigarette.

411
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,480
But the hospital won't allow it.

412
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,440
So smelling it is enough.

413
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:50,200
I've got some.

414
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,000
Want one?

415
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:53,440
Sure.

416
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:54,720
Come on, hurry.

417
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:55,240
Give me one.

418
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:00,240
Don't sneak around.

419
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,480
You...

420
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,600
Chocolate.

421
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:15,480
Fine, fine. Come on.

422
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:19,400
You don't know how to smoke?

423
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,240
One look and I can tell.

424
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,000
I'll teach you. Come on.

425
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:24,720
Move your hand forward.

426
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:25,440
Hold it further forward.

427
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,600
Here, near the front.

428
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:28,200
Relax.

429
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:29,160
Relax.

430
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,280
Make it natural, you know?

431
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:02,720
No, I don't...

432
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:03,480
I'm not finished with this one.

433
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,600
Have another.

434
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:05,720
Right. Do it yourself.

435
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:08,600
Oh no.

436
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:09,880
Go, go, go.

437
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:23,440
Dongzi.

438
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:26,240
What's wrong?

439
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,440
Doctor!

440
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:29,520
What's wrong?

441
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:30,480
Yi!

442
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:31,720
My heart feels wrong.

443
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:32,560
Yi!

444
00:18:37,560 --> 00:18:38,040
Dadong! Xiaomei!

445
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:38,800
Xiaomei!

446
00:18:40,360 --> 00:18:40,800
Xiaomei!

447
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:41,480
I'm here.

448
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:41,920
Xiaomei.

449
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,240
I'm here.

450
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:43,520
Come on.

451
00:18:46,840 --> 00:18:47,160
Xiaomei.

452
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,160
Move the family member away.

453
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:48,720
Family, step back.

454
00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:49,360
Step back.

455
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,040
Xiaomei! Xiaomei!

456
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:57,920
Family, make room.

457
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:58,560
Make room.

458
00:18:58,800 --> 00:18:59,280
Move aside. Move aside.

459
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:03,400
Moist rales in both lungs.

460
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,120
BP and oxygen saturation keep dropping.

461
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:06,080
Turn the oxygen up to max.

462
00:19:06,560 --> 00:19:07,360
Give one painkiller first.

463
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,200
One painkiller.

464
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,080
Open another IV line.

465
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:09,760
IV line.

466
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:10,800
Forty milligrams Lasix, IV push.

467
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:11,800
Notify the ICU.

468
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:12,800
Prepare for intubation.

469
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:13,120
Got it.

470
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,080
Dadong.

471
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,360
In such a short time,

472
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:27,200
his heart function has progressed to class IV.

473
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,080
It's advancing too fast.

474
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,480
We need to act.

475
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:31,800
As usual,

476
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,840
use mechanical support.

477
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:34,000
We need a cardiac surgery consult.

478
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:34,600
Invite them.

479
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:35,680
Okay.

480
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:40,480
On admission,

481
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,480
he had a respiratory infection.

482
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:43,000
Echocardiography showed

483
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,160
marked septal hypertrophy,

484
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,120
systolic anterior motion of the mitral valve,

485
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,760
but the left ventricle was significantly enlarged.

486
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:49,000
Cardiac MRI showed obvious myocardial fibrosis.

487
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:49,760
We can confirm this is

488
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:51,120
acute heart failure in end-stage

489
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,160
hypertrophic cardiomyopathy.

490
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,520
The patient's condition now meets

491
00:19:54,600 --> 00:19:55,840
the criteria for heart transplant.

492
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,080
We're planning to

493
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:57,800
register him in the system

494
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,160
and get him on the donor heart list.

495
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:00,400
Agreed.

496
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,400
What do we do now?

497
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,080
No one can say

498
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:05,920
when a donor will appear.

499
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:07,480
His blood pressure is so low now.

500
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:08,680
Standard anti-heart-failure drugs

501
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,040
can't even be given at target doses.

502
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:13,120
I think we should first consider

503
00:20:15,280 --> 00:20:16,160
left ventricular assist support.

504
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,480
LVAD is possible,

505
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,600
but I think for now,

506
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,400
ECMO

507
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,080
may be more suitable.

508
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:25,480
Lu Dadong is still young

509
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,360
with no other underlying disease.

510
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:28,040
This acute left-sided heart failure

511
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:28,880
was triggered by infection.

512
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:30,280
With ECMO support,

513
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,160
if we can increase the dosage,

514
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:32,480
there's still hope.

515
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:33,800
Of course we can use

516
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:34,160
ECMO.

517
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:34,720
But the problem is,

518
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:35,000
ECMO

519
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,360
is only a bridging measure.

520
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,120
If he doesn't improve after that,

521
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,200
we'll still need LVAD.

522
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,400
Why add an unnecessary step?

523
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:40,440
LVAD

524
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,520
is an invasive procedure after all.

525
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,480
And it's expensive.

526
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:44,360
Considering their finances,

527
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:46,080
I think a step-by-step approach is better.

528
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:46,680
And ECMO

529
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:47,520
doesn't cost money?

530
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:50,120
For critically ill patients like this,

531
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:51,880
cardiac surgery generally doesn't recommend

532
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:52,800
taking it slow.

533
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:53,840
We prefer

534
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:55,200
a simpler and more efficient approach

535
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,720
to relieve the patient's suffering

536
00:20:56,760 --> 00:20:57,160
and remove the hidden risks.

537
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:58,480
This cautious approach,

538
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,520
testing every step before moving,

539
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,600
may be safer procedurally,

540
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:02,760
but if it fails,

541
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,400
the patient suffers twice

542
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:05,480
and spends even more.

543
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:07,680
Exactly.

544
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:08,680
So it's unnecessary.

545
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,160
Xiao Lin.

546
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,120
After all,

547
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:12,720
the patient is in cardiology.

548
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,000
We're only giving advice.

549
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:15,720
The final discussion and decision

550
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:16,760
still belongs to Director Zhou and the family.

551
00:21:18,120 --> 00:21:19,000
Thank you, Director Sheng.

552
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:21,200
I'll communicate carefully with the family.

553
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:23,080
The final decision is still theirs.

554
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,280
If we need help later,

555
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,840
we'll come consult surgery again.

556
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:28,480
No, Director...

557
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:29,280
That's it.

558
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,440
When you're done later,

559
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:31,200
come to my office.

560
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:31,920
I need to talk to you.

561
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,560
Director Zhou, let's leave it there.

562
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:47,920
I saw an application

563
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:48,680
in the office system.

564
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:49,680
You want a multi-site practice permit.

565
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:50,880
What?

566
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,240
Is Dongli's workload

567
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,240
not full enough for you?

568
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:55,840
No.

569
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:57,360
Well...

570
00:21:57,760 --> 00:21:59,400
I did apply for multi-site practice,

571
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:00,800
but it's because

572
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,200
previously,

573
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:03,280
from our department,

574
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:04,080
our Director Zhao Yuliang

575
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,200
is now at Dongmu Hospital.

576
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:06,840
He called me

577
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:08,240
and said he's overwhelmed there,

578
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,400
so he hoped I could help out.

579
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:10,760
So I thought...

580
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:14,440
It's fine.

581
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:15,280
If you don't approve,

582
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:16,200
I don't mind.

583
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:17,000
Then I just won't go.

584
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:18,000
Is your nephew's side

585
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:18,680
short of money?

586
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,120
How did you know?

587
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,120
I only just learned

588
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,400
the details of your family situation.

589
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,000
Xiaorui

590
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,480
is preparing for a heart transplant.

591
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,920
Since he was diagnosed,

592
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:41,480
I've been doing

593
00:22:41,520 --> 00:22:42,480
heart transplant surgeries everywhere

594
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:43,600
to build up my qualifications.

595
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:44,840
Recently,

596
00:22:45,280 --> 00:22:46,480
he was listed for a donor too.

597
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:48,160
So,

598
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:50,280
I'm just planning ahead.

599
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:52,840
You also paid a lot

600
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,520
for your brother's situation before, right?

601
00:22:58,800 --> 00:22:59,560
I'll sign it.

602
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,360
But you must guarantee

603
00:23:02,560 --> 00:23:03,600
your normal work at the hospital.

604
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,200
I promise.

605
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:06,400
I absolutely promise.

606
00:23:08,080 --> 00:23:09,240
A person's energy is limited.

607
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,440
You have to consider your health

608
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:12,400
and your actual situation.

609
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,160
Do what you can.

610
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,400
We're in the same department.

611
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:17,080
That makes us family too.

612
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:18,880
If you need anything, just say so.

613
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,120
Thank you, Director.

614
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:27,040
It went through!

615
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:29,360
Sit.

616
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:32,120
There's more?

617
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:34,240
Lu Dadong is, after all,

618
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,240
a cardiology patient.

619
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:36,800
The final plan

620
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,040
has to be decided

621
00:23:38,160 --> 00:23:39,240
by them, the patient and family.

622
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:40,800
We just need

623
00:23:41,240 --> 00:23:41,840
to give our opinion.

624
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:45,200
But the treatment plan for the patient

625
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:46,560
must be the optimal one.

626
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,480
Director, don't worry.

627
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:51,600
Zhou Xiaofeng and I know each other well.

628
00:23:52,040 --> 00:23:53,000
He's always been like this.

629
00:23:53,120 --> 00:23:54,200
Overly cautious in everything.

630
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,800
Now that he's in charge, he's even more conservative.

631
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,400
I heard about it.

632
00:23:58,280 --> 00:23:59,440
Earlier, when Lu Dadong couldn't be found,

633
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:00,600
you wanted to call the police,

634
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:01,480
but he wouldn't let you.

635
00:24:02,360 --> 00:24:02,760
Exactly.

636
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:05,040
And before, when the cardiology nurse

637
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:05,480
made a mistake,

638
00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:06,800
I said a few words and he got upset.

639
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,720
A new leader needs

640
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,760
to unite the team.

641
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:13,920
Head Nurse Shen is senior,

642
00:24:14,080 --> 00:24:15,840
and famously strong-willed.

643
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:16,800
Director Zhou

644
00:24:17,520 --> 00:24:19,200
needs a good relationship with Nursing.

645
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,440
If he offends the nurses,

646
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:21,680
his work will be hard to carry out.

647
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:26,080
I know you're good brothers,

648
00:24:26,800 --> 00:24:28,480
but he has just taken office

649
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,240
and needs authority.

650
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,040
If you keep challenging him,

651
00:24:36,360 --> 00:24:36,720
it will affect his work too.

652
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:37,800
All right.

653
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,040
I understand.

654
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,160
Director.

655
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,480
This sparkling water is pretty good.

656
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:05,200
Can I have another glass?

657
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:07,760
Sleep, sleep, sleep.

658
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:10,080
All you do is sleep every day.

659
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,920
Didn't you sleep enough at home?

660
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:16,920
It's time to wake up.

661
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:18,800
Director Zhou told me

662
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:21,160
about some assist device and some membrane.

663
00:25:22,560 --> 00:25:23,760
I can't even put

664
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:24,600
a screen protector on my phone.

665
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,360
I don't understand any of it.

666
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:28,160
Dadong.

667
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:29,600
Wake up.

668
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,120
I thought

669
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:37,480
once we got married,

670
00:25:38,360 --> 00:25:39,720
I could sign for you.

671
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:43,240
What if I sign the wrong thing?

672
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:48,080
Which one should I choose?

673
00:25:58,080 --> 00:25:59,880
Stop sleeping.

674
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,800
Wake up and tell me.

675
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:04,880
Which one should I choose?

676
00:26:08,560 --> 00:26:09,400
Dadong.

677
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:12,240
Liang Mei.

678
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,040
Come here.

679
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,160
I've been watching

680
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,560
all of Dadong's indicators.

681
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,160
They're stabilizing now.

682
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,120
Although he can't speak

683
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:33,920
to you right now,

684
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:35,280
his body

685
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:36,520
is working hard to recover.

686
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,160
Dr. Fang.

687
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:47,440
I'm scared.

688
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,480
Don't be scared.

689
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:53,120
If I choose wrong for him,

690
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,600
what do I do?

691
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:55,600
Don't be scared.

692
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,760
You've been through so many difficulties.

693
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,240
Didn't you face them together?

694
00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:02,200
How about this?

695
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,760
After he is extubated and wakes up,

696
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,800
talk it over with him

697
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,120
then, okay?

698
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,200
You should rest for a while too.

699
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,920
Liang Mei can't make a decision now.

700
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:36,000
Based on the current situation,

701
00:27:36,120 --> 00:27:37,480
we can try extubation tomorrow.

702
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,360
Then we'll see what he wants

703
00:27:39,360 --> 00:27:40,040
and discuss it again.

704
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,240
Let's see what he chooses after he wakes up.

705
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:46,120
Bro.

706
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,520
What's wrong with your neck?

707
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,440
Allergy.

708
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:50,000
Hives.

709
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,440
When I went to Guizhou,

710
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,480
I probably wasn't used to the environment.

711
00:27:52,480 --> 00:27:53,520
It flares up now and then.

712
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:57,440
It's fine. It'll be better in a few days.

713
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,040
You've been back for so long.

714
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:00,840
Why is it still so bad?

715
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:03,120
Maybe I haven't rested well lately.

716
00:28:04,800 --> 00:28:05,800
It's fine. I've applied medicine.

717
00:28:06,280 --> 00:28:07,760
If it keeps recurring,

718
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,160
you should see dermatology properly.

719
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:10,160
I'll make you an appointment.

720
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:10,920
No need.

721
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,480
I still have several interventions. I have to go.

722
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,480
The Hainan stem cell therapy

723
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:16,120
research team

724
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,360
I've already signed Xiaorui up for it.

725
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,240
Tell him for me.

726
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:19,360
Okay.

727
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,120
Really?

728
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,120
Stem cell therapy has just received

729
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,600
clinical trial approval in China.

730
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,520
Hainan Island?

731
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,200
I've never been there.

732
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:32,360
When are we going?

733
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:34,280
Don't get too excited.

734
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:35,360
After we go,

735
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,160
whether it works or not

736
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:36,800
is still hard to say.

737
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,880
Then let's try it.

738
00:28:39,160 --> 00:28:40,600
I made some money

739
00:28:40,800 --> 00:28:41,680
selling plants and handicrafts anyway.

740
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,280
Let's treat it as a trip.

741
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:44,440
My treat.

742
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:48,880
Thank you, Boss Rui.

743
00:28:51,120 --> 00:28:51,520
By the way,

744
00:28:52,360 --> 00:28:53,480
has Dongzi's treatment plan

745
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,000
been decided?

746
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,440
Not yet.

747
00:28:58,080 --> 00:28:59,440
Liang Mei still hasn't made up her mind.

748
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:01,160
She wants to wait until Big Winter Melon

749
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:02,240
is stable,

750
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,080
then discuss it with him before deciding.

751
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,160
I support Dongzi

752
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,160
trying not to get the LVAD.

753
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:12,440
Why?

754
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,160
Think about it.

755
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:17,000
Having a machine in your chest long-term

756
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,840
and carrying batteries all the time...

757
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,480
How hard would life be?

758
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:21,920
If it were me,

759
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:23,080
I get nervous

760
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:24,480
when my phone drops below 50 percent.

761
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,080
I'd be anxious to death.

762
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,480
Don't reject it too much.

763
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:32,000
LVAD technology

764
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,120
is getting more advanced now.

765
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:34,880
It has little impact on daily life.

766
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:36,720
I know.

767
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:37,920
But I still don't want it.

768
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:40,360
Call me fussy if you want.

769
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:42,800
If that day really comes,

770
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,400
I won't get one.

771
00:29:44,560 --> 00:29:45,400
Don't try to persuade me either.

772
00:29:46,800 --> 00:29:47,600
Do you hear me?

773
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,880
The longer I have this disease,

774
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,480
the more I hope

775
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:00,000
I can still live

776
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,200
like a normal person.

777
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:18,360
Director, off work?

778
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:25,600
Director Zhou.

779
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:31,520
Why are you here?

780
00:30:32,560 --> 00:30:33,120
Waiting for you.

781
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:35,400
I knew

782
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,840
you must be very busy lately.

783
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,080
If I texted or called,

784
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:39,120
I probably couldn't get you out.

785
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:40,480
So I waited here and tried my luck,

786
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:42,680
to see if you'd do me the honor

787
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,080
of having a simple meal with me.

788
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:47,800
I saw you went into surgery

789
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:48,680
at three this afternoon.

790
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:49,840
Why are you only coming out now?

791
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:51,160
You must've been so busy

792
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,680
you haven't eaten at all, right?

793
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:55,160
An extra case came in.

794
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:56,680
So...

795
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:58,480
you waited here five hours?

796
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:00,000
Yes.

797
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:01,800
I was afraid I'd miss you.

798
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,480
I'm so hungry now

799
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:05,840
my stomach's touching my back.

800
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:06,920
Please do me the honor

801
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,480
of having dinner with me.

802
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:21,160
I come to this place often.

803
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:23,000
It's a hole-in-the-wall,

804
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,800
but the owner is very nice.

805
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,680
She never serves

806
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,480
pre-cooked food.

807
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,480
Everything is stir-fried fresh.

808
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:28,400
It's got wok hei.

809
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:31,040
See what you'd like to eat.

810
00:31:32,040 --> 00:31:33,160
You order. Anything is fine.

811
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:35,080
Then I'll order

812
00:31:35,120 --> 00:31:36,160
some of their specialties.

813
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,000
Try them first.

814
00:31:41,120 --> 00:31:41,480
Okay.

815
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:46,880
The usual.

816
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,400
Even if it's a hole-in-the-wall,

817
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,440
we still need some ceremony.

818
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,280
Aren't these the enamel mugs

819
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:01,200
from the school anniversary?

820
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,400
Yes.

821
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:03,680
After buying the red wine,

822
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:04,840
I had no money left for glasses.

823
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:06,160
Let's make do.

824
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,040
Same habit,

825
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:12,840
overall upgraded.

826
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:13,840
Isn't this

827
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:15,120
to celebrate your promotion?

828
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:28,800
Director Zhou.

829
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:29,800
Congratulations on your promotion.

830
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:31,480
Cheers.

831
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,400
I really think

832
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,400
you're admirable.

833
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:41,920
Not even forty,

834
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:43,200
and already director of a major department.

835
00:32:45,040 --> 00:32:45,760
Acting director.

836
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,440
It's all the same to me.

837
00:32:49,480 --> 00:32:51,160
You've always moved toward your ideal

838
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:52,200
step by step,

839
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,680
steadily and surely.

840
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:56,680
Congratulations.

841
00:33:09,120 --> 00:33:09,760
What about you?

842
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,000
Me?

843
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:13,160
Why did you stop being a doctor

844
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:14,800
and become a pharma rep?

845
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:19,880
Have you wanted to ask me that

846
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,000
since the first moment you saw me?

847
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,440
Yes.

848
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:25,000
Actually,

849
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:27,880
like many people who switch careers,

850
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:29,800
I just wanted more

851
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,160
time for myself

852
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:32,480
and to make more money.

853
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:35,160
Did you make it?

854
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:39,840
I'm working on it.

855
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:45,240
Actually, I know

856
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:48,040
many people look at our profession

857
00:33:48,240 --> 00:33:49,440
with tinted glasses,

858
00:33:49,800 --> 00:33:50,760
especially female sales reps.

859
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,080
But I don't care.

860
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,520
I earn my money honestly.

861
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,000
Let them say whatever they want.

862
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:58,720
I don't care.

863
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,600
That's your style.

864
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:05,120
And

865
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:07,240
although I changed careers,

866
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:08,440
I haven't left my profession.

867
00:34:08,600 --> 00:34:10,040
Nor have I betrayed

868
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:11,720
my original reason

869
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:13,480
for studying medicine

870
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,840
and wanting to be a doctor.

871
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:19,800
To original intentions.

872
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,800
To ideals.

873
00:34:25,680 --> 00:34:26,800
To ideals.

874
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,280
To ideals.

875
00:35:10,200 --> 00:35:11,280
We're drinking pretty fast.

876
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,000
How about two bottles of beer?

877
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:15,880
Sure.

878
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:17,840
Sister Xia.

879
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:18,920
Two bottles of beer.

880
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,400
Coming.

881
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:22,800
By the way,

882
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,080
I've spoken with

883
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:26,480
my partners at Mai'anpei.

884
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,440
In the future, free programs

885
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:30,160
and department meetings

886
00:35:30,160 --> 00:35:31,160
will give priority

887
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:33,040
to grassroots hospitals in Guizhou.

888
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,800
We'll direct more resources to them

889
00:35:34,880 --> 00:35:37,680
and help take some pressure off you.

890
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,200
Beer.

891
